# Architecture: Scan Execution

**Version:** 1.0
**Status:** Draft
**Spec:** [Feature Spec](../1-requirements/scan_execution/scan_execution.spec)

## Components

| Component | Traces To | Description |
|-----------|-----------|-------------|
| FR-300 handler | STK-02 -> `api/scans.rs` | The API shall accept scan requests and execute them asynchronously, invoking the doc-engine library's `scan_with_config()` function with the project's configured root path and the requested scope. |
| FR-301 handler | STK-02, STK-10 -> `api/scans.rs` | Trigger struct-engine scan |
| FR-302 handler | STK-02 -> `api/ws.rs`, `ui/scans/` | Real-time scan progress |
| FR-303 handler | STK-02, STK-03 -> `api/scans.rs` | Scan result retrieval |
| FR-304 handler | STK-02 -> `api/scans.rs` | Scan filtering options |
| FR-305 handler | STK-12 -> `api/scans.rs` | Scan history |

